### ===============================
### [POST] Izveido darbību tipu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "approve",
  "label": "Apstiprināšana",
  "description": "Versijas apstiprināšanas darbība"
}

###

### [POST] Izveido žurnāla ierakstu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseVersion": { "id": "0502af48-92ef-4cbd-86c5-f5b220996573" },
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "action": { "id": 1 },
  "comment": "Apstiprināts ar korekcijām"
}

###

### [POST] Izveido komentāru
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseVersion": { "id": "0502af48-92ef-4cbd-86c5-f5b220996573" },
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "comment": "Nepieciešams papildināt anotāciju"
}

### ===============================
### [GET] Iegūst visus ierakstus

GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-actions
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-logs
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-comments

### ===============================
### [PUT] Atjauno žurnāla ierakstu ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-logs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseVersion": { "id": "0502af48-92ef-4cbd-86c5-f5b220996573" },
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "action": { "id": 1 },
  "comment": "Atjaunināts ieraksts ar piezīmēm"
}

###

### [PUT] Atjauno komentāru ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-comments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseVersion": { "id": "0502af48-92ef-4cbd-86c5-f5b220996573" },
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "comment": "Piezīme atjaunināta pēc saskaņošanas"
}

### ===============================
### [DELETE] Dzēš ierakstus pēc ID

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-version-actions/1
###
